<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Pages légales — Sonny Court</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Accès rapide aux pages légales de Sonny Court : conditions d'utilisation, politique de confidentialité et mentions légales."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #070b16;
        --card: #0d1324;
        --text: #e2e8f0;
        --muted: #94a3b8;
        --border: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.22);
        --glow: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.24);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: Inter, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(900px 500px at 20% 0%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2), transparent 65%),
          radial-gradient(800px 500px at 100% 100%, rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.14), transparent 60%),
          var(--bg);
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        padding: 28px 16px;
      }

      .wrap {
        width: min(760px, 100%);
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01));
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 22px;
        padding: clamp(24px, 4vw, 36px);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 10px;
        font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 4vw, 2.2rem);
        line-height: 1.2;
      }

      .sub {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.55;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 12px;
      }

      .sticker-btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 10px;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.3);
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #eff6ff;
        background: linear-gradient(140deg, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.2), rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.52));
        font-weight: 600;
        transition: transform 0.15s ease, border-color 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.15s ease;
      }

      .sticker-btn:hover {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        border-color: rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.6);
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.25), 0 10px 30px var(--glow);
      }

      .arrow {
        color: #93c5fd;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="wrap">
      <h1>Pages légales</h1>
      <p class="sub">Accès rapide à toutes les pages légales présentes dans le footer.</p>

      <div class="grid">
        <a class="sticker-btn" href="/conditions-utilisation/">
          Conditions d'utilisation
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a class="sticker-btn" href="/confidentialite/">
          Politique de confidentialité
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
        <a class="sticker-btn" href="/mentions-legales/">
          Mentions légales
          <span class="arrow">→</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
